    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Why is the `href` in your example https://www.algolia.com/users/sign_in instead of the link you want to go to? e.g. if the url you put in Algolia are complete urls, then do:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"{{href}}\">\r\n```\r\n\r\nor whatever the name of the attribute is. If the URL is relative, then:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"https://base.com/{{path}}\">\r\n```\r\n\r\nIs that what you meant?",
